Title: Something Not Ruined
Description: Alright, I'll come with you. Show you how to do this properly. If I'm up, we might as well stock up on taro. Can't rely on adventurers to do delicate work, I suppose.
ObjectivesText: Harvest 6 taro with the chef. Properly, this time.
RewardText: Much better. This will last for a while. If you want to eat, though, I'll need a little more help.
